  Locus:
    Page: 149
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Faith
---
Blind faith should be turned into rational faith. Faith without
understanding is only blind faith. Devotion is the development of faith.
Knowledge is the development of devotion. Faith leads to the final spiritual
experience. Whatever a person strongly believes in, that he experiences
and becomes.
